room_title: Escape room "The Time Keeper" by The LOST Escape Room in Charleston (WV)

room_description: Events throughout time have been safeguarded since Ancient Egypt. The Time Keepers now need you to help protect an ancient artifact from a sinister circle and prevent catastrophic history-altering events. Can you pass the trials to become a Time Keeper?
